{"id":26016,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/26016","type":2,"name":"ゾイドフューザーズ","name_cn":"机兽超世纪","summary":"生活在蔚蓝之都（Blue City）的少年——RD，驾驶父亲遗留的长牙狮零式参加Zoid格斗赛（Zoid Battle），并一直为自己的梦想——成为顶级的Zi战士（Zi Fighter）、寻找父亲所说的传说中的Zoid而奋斗着。然而，要参加Zoid格斗赛也不是件轻松地事情。为了赚取比赛的出场费，RD和与自己一样属于极速风暴（Mach Storm）的同伴们一起接手各种任务。\r\n突然间，一个被称为“Unison Zoid”的新事物出现在人们的面前。“Unison Zoid”是数个Zoid的合体，合体的能力相比通常的Zoid有了数倍的提升。“Unison Zoid”的出现令Zoid格斗赛焕然一新。\r\n随着长牙狮零式也能进行融合，一个又一个的强敌出现在RD面前。同时，珊朵拉率领的所属破坏榔头（Savage Hammer）的RD的劲敌——布雷德也与自己展开因缘的对决。在这期间，幕后巨大组织的阴影浮现了出来。隐藏在“Unison Zoid”背后的阴谋笼罩着蔚蓝之都，RD他们能够阻止组织的阴谋的得逞吗？","eps":[{"id":130322,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130322","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130323,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130323","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130324,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130324","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130325,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130325","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130326,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130326","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130327,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130327","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130328,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130328","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130329,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130329","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130330,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130330","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":130331,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/130331","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"